metadata.name: @fabriclord Metaverse ID
metadata.description:
Metaverse ID is an online handle that you own and control, tied to all your crypto wallets and assets.

In the past we used emails, Twitter or Instagram handles for presenting our online identity. Now things have changed and your Metaverse ID will allow you to own your handle and easily communicate with others in the Metaverse, while retaining your privacy.
